Change Description:
Manual DNs (not PGIed) will have specific SO-Lots pegged at the time of DN creation. FSSD Fab POLP dynamic lot pegging algorithm need to be enhanced to retain these SO-Lot combination and not use these SO and Lots during dynamic lot pegging.. Design Change – (a) DN based Fixed Pegging : Peg the SO and Lots based on DNs which have not been shipped; 
(b). Factory based Fixed Pegging : Peg the SO and Lots based on Demand Pegging Lot Attribute from factory;
(c ). Look for lots in WH which have been pegged to SO in last run and peg the Lot to same SO.
For remaining lots, run the dynamic lot pegging algorithm as per existing capability;
